INSERT INTO Tasks (TaskID, CompanyName, date_started, date_finished, details, header, Staff, Bug) VALUES (2761, 'Tower Hamlets Healthcare Trust', '2001-09-13 00:00:00', '2001-10-01 00:00:00', 'logged by Steve. Linking ph_hist to ph_w_don to include detail_1 in report. Told him if links to table which may not contain related records from master table report will only display records that are in both tables. Will require outer join, though pharaoh won\'t do outer joins. He said report ran fine before upgrade. He will email copy of old and new report for me to investigate. Testing shows report does display records in one table if linked to another table where they don\'t exist but only if report does not contain field from that second table, then no records show. Steve has checked that no users have deleted work_done text. Says problem in transferring stuff from wk_done to ph_w_don, ie 74284 and 74280. Told him I will look into.KH 180901- tried to duplicate situation of work done text being lost during transfer process. Tried with and without delay transfer but work done text transferred fine. KH 270901 - unable to consistantly manu UNION sql writtten in Crystal to work so will use sub-reporting. Created basic sub-report and linked to main report similar to Steve requiements and emailled to him. Will have a look and let me know require any changes. Re missing work done text told him need to be told when first happens. Task closed.WW - Mon. 01/10/2001 - Task reopened. Steve rang today asking about the report. I did\'nt realise Kate had sent him a crystal report. So as the ph_j_det table should be identical to the ph_w_don table, as the job details are getting, will be now anyway, tranferred straight into the work done text, then he can link to this table instead of the ph_w_don table. Steve seems happy with this solution. Task closed.', 'Crystal report not reporting correct information', 'Kate Hamilton', 0);
