INSERT INTO Tasks (TaskID, CompanyName, date_started, date_finished, details, header, Staff, Bug) VALUES (2766, 'Parliamentary Works Directorate', '2001-09-24 00:00:00', '2001-10-16 00:00:00', 'FORMS:[inv_rep.fs] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[ret_to_sup.fs] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[purch_inv.fs] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[purch_inv2.fs] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[inv_no_grn.fs] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[inv_nogrn2.fs] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[grn_invenq.fs] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[rep_certs.fs] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[ac_crte2i.fs] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.REPORTS:[supp_pays.rp] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[sub_cons.rp] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[inv_rep.rp] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[inv_rep.rs] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[purch_inv.rp] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[inv_no_grn.rp] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[stk_purchs.rp] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[rep_certs.rp] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[ac_crte2i.rp] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended.[pwd_crte2i.rp] : got, amended, compiled, tested, put, .changes ammended. (Done twice as first time there was an error).SCHEMA:[fx_dets] : $PHABASE/lib/schema.361 ammended, tested.[grn_dets] : $PHABASE/lib/schema.361 ammended, tested.The grn_dets and fx_dets tables use the invoice_number char (12) field. There is a report - purch_inv.rp - printed from the purch_inv screen, which also uses the field. The fx_dets reports will have to be checked to see which of them use the invoice_number field